Design Patterns
---------------

-- It is a template for guiding structure.
-- Complement principles like SOLID, GRAPS and Clean Architecture 

Types
------

⦁	Creational -- Singleton, Factory, Abstract Factory, Builder, Prototype.
⦁	Structural -- Adapter, Facade, Composite, Decorator, Proxy, Bridge, Flyweight 
⦁	Behavioral -- Strategy, Observer, Command, State, Template Method, Iterator, Mediator, Chain of responsibility, Memento, Visitor


Most Used Patterns
------------------
⦁	Creational -- Singleton, Factory, Abstract Factory
⦁	Structural -- Adapter, Facade, Decorator, Proxy
⦁	Behavioral -- Strategy, Observer, Command, State
